<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rental Agreement</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 40px; color: #333; }
        .container { width: 80%; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h1 { text-align: center; color: #007bff; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 24px; }
        .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .section-title { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; text-decoration: underline; }
        .content { margin-left: 20px; }
        .signature-block { margin-top: 50px; display: flex; justify-content: space-around; }
        .signature-item { text-align: center; width: 45%; }
        .signature-line { border-top: 1px solid #000; width: 200px; margin: 5px auto; padding-top: 5px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 50px; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; color: #666; }
        .bold { font-weight: bold; }
        .italic { font-style: italic; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>RENTAL AGREEMENT</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <p>This Rental Agreement is made and entered into on this <span class="bold">{{ agreement_start_date | default('[Agreement Start Date]') }}</span></p>
            <p>BETWEEN:</p>
            <p><span class="bold">{{ landlord_name | default('[Landlord Name]') }}</span>, son/daughter of [Father's Name], residing at <span class="bold">{{ landlord_address | default('[Landlord Address]') }}</span> (hereinafter referred to as "the Landlord").</p>
            <p>AND</p>
            <p><span class="bold">{{ tenant_name | default('[Tenant Name]') }}</span>, son/daughter of [Father's Name], residing at <span class="bold">{{ tenant_address | default('[Tenant Address]') }}</span> (hereinafter referred to as "the Tenant").</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Property Details:</div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>The Landlord hereby agrees to let out and the Tenant hereby agrees to take on rent the property located at:</p>
                <p><span class="bold">{{ property_address | default('[Property Address]') | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Terms of Agreement:</div>
            <div class="content">
                <p><span class="bold">1. Rent:</span> The monthly rent for the said property shall be INR <span class="bold">{{ rent_amount | default('[Rent Amount]') }}</span>, payable on or before the 5th day of each calendar month.</p>
                <p><span class="bold">2. Security Deposit:</span> The Tenant shall pay a security deposit of INR <span class="bold">{{ security_deposit | default('[Security Deposit]') }}</span>, which shall be refundable at the time of vacating the premises, subject to deductions for damages or unpaid dues.</p>
                <p><span class="bold">3. Lease Period:</span> This agreement shall be for a period of [Duration, e.g., 11 months] commencing from <span class="bold">{{ agreement_start_date | default('[Agreement Start Date]') }}</span> and ending on <span class="bold">{{ agreement_end_date | default('[Agreement End Date]') }}</span>.</p>
                <p><span class="bold">4. Other Terms and Conditions:</span></p>
                <p>{{ terms_and_conditions | default('[Terms and Conditions]') | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties have executed this Agreement on the date first above written.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="signature-item">
                <p>_________________________</p>
                <p><span class="bold">{{ signature_landlord | default('[Landlord Signature]') }}</span></p>
                <p>(Landlord)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-item">
                <p>_________________________</p>
                <p><span class="bold">{{ signature_tenant | default('[Tenant Signature]') }}</span></p>
                <p>(Tenant)</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Note: This is a draft rental agreement. It is advisable to consult with a legal professional and register the agreement as per local laws.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
